OL,3,CStephen McCullagh to appeal 31-year
OL,4,Csentence for Natalie McNally murder
OL,6,FThe man convicted of the murder of
OL,7,FNatalie McNally is to appeal against
OL,8,Fthe 31-year sentence he received.
OL,10,FStephen McCullagh staged a fake
OL,11,FYouTube gaming livestream to provide
OL,12,Fan alibi for the murder of his
OL,13,Fpregnant partner in December 2022.
OL,15,FThe 36-year-old was told by a judge at
OL,16,FBelfast Crown Court earlier this month
OL,17,Fthat he will serve at least 31 years
OL,18,Fin prison for the killing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
