OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782913702
OL,3,CStephen McCullagh to appeal 31-year
OL,4,Csentence for Natalie McNally murder
OL,6,FThe Public Prosecution Service in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland has been notified
OL,8,Fthat an appeal against the sentence
OL,9,Fhas now been lodged.
OL,11,FMcCullagh of Woodland Gardens,
OL,12,FLisburn, was found guilty of the
OL,13,Fmurder by a jury earlier this year.
OL,15,FMs McNally, 32, had been 15 weeks
OL,16,Fpregnant when she was subjected to
OL,17,Fwhat judge Mr Justice Kinney described
OL,18,Fas a "brutal and frenzied attack".
OL,26,@zD@FOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
