PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782913702
OL,3,CStephen McCullagh to appeal 31-year
OL,4,Csentence for Natalie McNally murder
OL,6,FThe judge said the staged livestream
OL,7,Fof McCullagh playing computer games on
OL,8,Fthe night he killed Ms McNally was an
OL,9,F"integral" part of his murder plan.
OL,11,FMcCullagh denied the murder to
OL,12,Fdetectives, claiming he had been
OL,13,Flivestreaming on his YouTube channel
OL,14,Fat the time she died.
OL,16,FBut police experts discovered the six-
OL,17,Fhour stream had actually been filmed
OL,18,Ffour days before and broadcast as live
OL,19,Fon December 18 2022, the night Ms
OL,20,FMcNally was killed.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
