PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782913702
OL,3,CStephen McCullagh to appeal 31-year
OL,4,Csentence for Natalie McNally murder
OL,6,FThe judge said the staged livestream
OL,7,Fhad been "carefully curated to appear
OL,8,Fas if it was streaming live and to
OL,9,Fprovide the defendant a carefully
OL,10,Fplanned complete alibi to the murder".
OL,12,FThe judge said when considering the
OL,13,Ftariff he assessed McCullagh's
OL,14,Fculpability as "extremely high".
OL,16,F"The defendant did not just kill
OL,17,FNatalie McNally, her unborn child also
OL,18,Fdied as a result of the murderous
OL,19,Fassault," said the judge.
OL,26,@oD@JOUrD@eO]vD@POUvD@_O]xD@AOU{D@IO]
