CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782913702
OL,3,CStephen McCullagh to appeal 31-year
OL,4,Csentence for Natalie McNally murder
OL,6,FSetting the minimum 31-year prison
OL,7,Fterm, the judge said the sentence
OL,8,Fpassed "cannot possibly reflect the
OL,9,Fvalue of Natalie's life, or indeed
OL,10,Fthat of her unborn child, Dean" or
OL,11,Fmeet the family's sense of "grief and
OL,12,Floss".
